text: C.D. Alcoyano is a football club which plays in Spain. Founded in 1928 it plays in Primera División RFEF – Group 2, holding home games in Estadio El Collao, with a 4,850-seat capacity. ==League position== Season League Position 2000/01 Tercera División 17th / Group 6 2001/02 Tercera División 10th / Group 6 2002/03 Tercera División 5th / Group 6 2003/04 Tercera División 2nd / Group 6 2004/05 Segunda División B 7th / Group 3 2005/06 Segunda División B 5th / Group 3 2006/07 Segunda División B 3rd / Group 3 2007/08 Segunda División B 9th / Group 3 2008/09 Segunda División B 1st / Group 3 ===Former position=== ==References== Category:1928 establishments in Spain Category:Spanish football clubs Category:Valencian Community
